<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1362233" n="1"/> 
<opener><salute><abbr>D<hi rend="sup">ne</hi></abbr> mihi plurimum colende</salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Post exacta lepide Bacchanalia, postque ex animo obliterata illinc suppedita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><sic>tata</sic><corr>ta</corr></choice> oblectamenta, in Matheseos mei veteris <rs type="person">amici</rs> gratiam paulatim redire
    <lb/>conatus sum. Consilium ineram sedulo et primo considerasse qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nos <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Veneti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>arum</rs> intercessere; quod jam factum esset, ni perfidi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> memori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> oblivioni tradita
    <lb/>fuissent. Oro igitur ut difficultatem quam de Resistenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Pendulorum mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vebas, et <rs type="biblio">Problemata</rs> illa a <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117601020" type="person">Monmort</rs> ex <rs key="place_VER-frankr" type="place">Galli<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs> ad te transmissa iterum
    <lb/>communices. Postquam eadem consideravero, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi occurrent tuo judicio
    <lb/>submittam. Vellem etiam certior fieri, an mecum jam adhuc consentis, Cele<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>berrimi <rs type="person">Patrui</rs> <rs type="biblio">Theorema pro conjiciendis curvarum areis in Series conver<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gentes</rs> non esse generalem, vel etiamnum dissentis. Ego in h<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>c de re opini<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>one firmatus sum, promptus tamen de sententi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> protenus discedere, ubi error
    <lb/>meus comparuerit. Quod si alias res novas Mathematicas aut Philosophicas
    <lb/>impert<del><gap/></del><add>i</add>eris, tanto magis me devinctum habebis. Nam siquidem familiaritatem
    <lb/>quotidianam neget locorum intervallum, eadem frequente Epistolarum reci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>procatione quodammodo compensetur; qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi multum promittit fructum,
    <lb/>tibique spero haud prorsus displicebit: cujusque hoc sit f<del><gap/></del><add>e</add>lix faustumque
    <lb/>principium, precatur</p>
  <closer><choice><abbr>D<hi rend="sup">nis</hi></abbr><expan>Dominationis</expan></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> 
    <lb/>servus humillimus
    <lb/><signed><rs key="pers_DE-588-117260266" type="person">Jacobus Stirling</rs></signed>
    <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1719-04-23">23. Aprilis 1719.</date>  <choice><abbr>S. N.</abbr><expan>Stylo Novo</expan></choice></dateline>
    <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den <date when="1719-04-27">27<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date></foreign></note>
  </closer>
<postscript>
<p>Clarissimo D<hi rend="sup">no</hi> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Poleni</rs> multam
  <lb/>oro a me dicas salutem.</p>
</postscript>
